Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.28,0:00:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the Millennium Puzzle complete,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The young boy Yugi Mutou became a master of the Dark Games.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was challenged by a person that has a Millennium Item like him,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the owner of the Millennium Eye, Pegasus, and went to the Duelist Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To save the soul of Sugoroku, that was stolen by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Together with his friends and with his other self.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.33,0:00:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A magazine page I can't finish reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to read it, but somehow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.07,0:00:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Game software is stacked in the corner of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.85,0:01:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't play them, will they become meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.78,0:01:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just beyond the table, and I'm trying to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.60,0:01:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A never changing facial expression is on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.92,0:01:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm right here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.17,0:01:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't reach, they can't reach, these feelings of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.97,0:01:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what's really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.56,0:01:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.20,0:01:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use your card to slit my throat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.51,0:01:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go, Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.08,0:01:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Elf Swordsman!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.65,0:01:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, you mustn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.52,0:02:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi! Return to your usual self!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...! You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.64,0:02:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.64,0:02:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of this game and my other...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.92,0:02:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Duel of Tears!\NFriendship"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Use your card to slit my throat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.73,0:03:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Here I go, Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.57,0:03:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Elf Swordsman!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It couldn't be helped... I had no other choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I continued the Duel, Kaiba-kun....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.77,0:03:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But by doing this, I stood in my other self's way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.25,0:03:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I became a burden...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without the other me, I can't do anything...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.73,0:03:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without him....
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.50,0:03:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I hadn't stopped Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, take my Star Chips.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:03:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was because you gave me one of your Star Chips\Nthat I got to play in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These belong to you, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not time to give up yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.32,0:04:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange, just do your best in the coming Duels!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Yugi. Take them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.37,0:04:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just sit there, at least {\i1}say{\i0} something!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you care about gramps!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to do something...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.30,0:04:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If this keeps up...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.44,0:04:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you all doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.57,0:04:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi... You collected 10 Star Chips?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... But it's about to be half that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.07,0:04:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pegasus... I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The flame of anger around him is clearly visible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This scene is beauty beyond description.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.40,0:05:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I particularly love the hatred charging\Npoint-blank at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.39,0:05:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi {\i1}lost{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't screw around with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.67,0:05:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be defeated without entering the castle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.73,0:05:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't accept that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that, then you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.73,0:05:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.92,0:05:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,16 Star Chips...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing... That's Mai Kujaku for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.73,0:05:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.99,0:05:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:06:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm paying you back what I owe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In return, you must battle me in the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.33,0:06:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.70,0:06:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just accept them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.17,0:06:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can enter the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I overrated you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because you lost {\i1}one{\i0} Duel, you lose your morale!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not so great after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi lost because I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you won't suck it up and enter
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.76,0:06:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how about we have a Duel right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll agree to that much, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.96,0:06:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.57,0:06:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san, {\i1}I'll{\i0} Duel with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.43,0:06:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I win...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,those Star Chips are {\i1}mine{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.96,0:06:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi oi, how can {\i1}you{\i0} win?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my responsibility to get Yugi into that castle no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san, fight {\i1}me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.50,0:07:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}really{\i0} think you can defeat me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will surely win!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.77,0:07:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I {\i1}have{\i0} to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as Yugi gets those chips...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.13,0:07:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's fine by me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I accept.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.97,0:07:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have a condition for this fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.40,0:07:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.53,0:07:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose, you will never again mutter a word\Nabout comrades or friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.99,0:07:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sorta...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.59,0:07:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The air feels tense...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.63,0:07:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel start!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go first!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.13,0:08:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The air's filled with tension...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.51,0:08:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I say it.... the tension feels\Ndifferent than other matches somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Petite Angel in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.23,0:08:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so weak~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.53,0:08:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that cute thing gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.46,0:08:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harpie Lady in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I play this card on the Field.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you seriously want to beat me, play something with a higher Attack than {\i1}that{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy's Treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.77,0:08:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.28,0:09:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amateurs really give one a headache...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.15,0:09:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not enough to {\i1}just{\i0}\N increase your Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.93,0:09:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Emissaries of Harmony's effect is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A Trap Card that renders all damage\Nto the opponent's monsters 0 for one turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That may become useful later on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.90,0:09:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a card.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.90,0:09:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She got that in a Playing Pack didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may help her win...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.98,0:09:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Dust!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her Attack is higher than the enemy...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.71,0:10:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card, Rose Whip activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.34,0:10:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This increases Harpie Lady's Attack by 300!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go, Harpie Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red Hell Whipper!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll defeat {\i1}me{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.56,0:10:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:10:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.33,0:11:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She taunted her opponent into attacking\Nonly to spring a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the enemy thought she had\N the advantage with the higher Attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she immediately activated her set card\Nto increase her Attack Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say it was your fault Yugi lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.35,0:11:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I hate the most about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.22,0:11:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop thinking so high of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not thinking highly of myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.69,0:11:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the fight starts, every Duelist is alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't rely on other's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.93,0:11:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can only trust yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.64,0:11:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi lost because he wasn't good enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.24,0:11:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.61,0:11:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you only win because of your friends,\Nwhat's the point in it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really think you can make Yugi win this way
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then it's the same as thinking high of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the next one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.72,0:11:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Another set card?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.66,0:12:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Friendship...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Friendship"...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,600)\i1}This is the proof of our friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.77,0:12:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right... My bond with everyone is more precious than anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's what makes a true "friendship".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I must protect this card no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.99,0:12:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.79,0:12:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.13,0:12:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll bet everything on this card!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.97,0:12:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll bet on our friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.60,0:12:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friendship! Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.81,0:12:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still think this type of\N monster can defeat me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harpie Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.94,0:12:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red Hell Whipper!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.12,0:12:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap Card activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:12:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emissaries of Harmony!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.83,0:13:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Anzu's not doing too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, weren't {\i1}you{\i0} beaten by Anzu countless times?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.81,0:13:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san, I'll show you how I'll protect\Nthis friendship until the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.25,0:13:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card represents our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you say,\N I believe in my friends....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.39,0:13:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... we've always stuck by each other....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we finally made it this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.90,0:13:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we can't press\N on without one of our group!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.24,0:13:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what that won't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:13:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:14:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you hear what Anzu just said?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.51,0:14:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to get you into the castle,\Nshe's betting everything on this Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even seeing that, can you still just give it all up that easily?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.26,0:14:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least win the Duel before you spout nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will {\i1}never{\i0} lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saint Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.44,0:14:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, the Magic Card Silver Bow and Arrow
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.71,0:14:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to increase Friendship's Attack\Nand Defense Points up by 300!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.32,0:14:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cyber Bondage!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This adds more armor to Harpy Lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and raises her Attack Points up by 500!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.76,0:14:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Undo Magic activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, there's still a huge gap\Nin strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.65,0:15:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure what you set...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'd better dispose of this one first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saint Magician is beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop spacing out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Saint Magician was destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.60,0:15:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You get to return a Magic Card from the Graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this level, it's a 100 years too soon for you to beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've said it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.51,0:15:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Foolish words like "comrade" and "friendship"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are the two words one must never say in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.68,0:15:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Win or lose, the cruelties of the world still remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.22,0:15:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So as long as one exists in this cruel world
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.69,0:15:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,many use their friends to relieve the pain of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.80,0:16:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, all you can rely on is {\i1}yourself{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When one is pushed into a corner during a Duel...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what is it they need more than anything to press on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.81,0:16:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is one's own strong will and determination!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your own determination...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.17,0:16:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Duelist lacking this courage
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.15,0:16:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will only end up betraying themselves\Nand their friend's expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I still want to protect my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.60,0:16:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to protect Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true in the end it's Yugi's decision whether he accepts them or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.60,0:16:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I want to do more than just cheer all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore no matter what you say,\NI {\i1}will{\i0} get Yugi into that castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.31,0:16:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.27,0:16:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect Yugi until the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.19,0:16:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm his comrade....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.19,0:17:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm his {\i1}friend{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.13,0:17:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.40,0:17:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you how I guard our friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you {\i1}can{\i0}, give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A Magic Card, Elf's Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It increases the Attack Points of a Light Attribute Monster by 400 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.45,0:17:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I also have an Undo Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai-san used this same card\Non her last turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.88,0:17:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's it! That way Silver Bow and Arrow would\Nincrease its Attack Points to 1600...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Also, with Elf's Light, its Attack will increase again to 2000...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Undo Magic will get rid of Cyber Bondage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.30,0:17:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.44,0:17:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card, Silver Bow and Arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.47,0:17:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It increases Friendship's Attack Points up by 300!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.91,0:17:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Following, I activate my\N second Magic Card, Elf's Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:18:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This increases Friendship's\N Attack Points again by 400!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.19,0:18:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm. Looks like the match is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.69,0:18:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use the Undo Magic card\N to destroy Cyber Bondage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.34,0:18:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.34,0:18:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.21,0:18:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silver Lightning Arrow!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harpie Lady is beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she's stronger than {\i1}you{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.63,0:18:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Alright.\N-Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.77,0:18:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's a Trap Card...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.41,0:18:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.38,0:18:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your heart was stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.14,0:19:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the match isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I lose my Harpie, my Duel is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My pride won't allow me to fight on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.59,0:19:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.59,0:19:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were amazing, Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san, that set card was\NHarpie's Feather--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop joking around!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.44,0:19:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't thanks to {\i1}you{\i0} that I lost you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's settle the score inside the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.35,0:19:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.08,0:19:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please use these to save your grandfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.39,0:19:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.92,0:19:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.76,0:19:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.63,0:19:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Duel with your own will and determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's a Duelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.27,0:19:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isn't that right, my other self?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be cheering you on until the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.24,0:20:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our friendship conquers all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.35,0:20:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how long are you gonna take?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.65,0:20:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't hurry you won't make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.42,0:20:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.99,0:20:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.05,0:20:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YEAH!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.52,0:20:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Into the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(128,140)}"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally made it to Pegasus' castle and the finals of the tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.30,0:20:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But before that, it seems Kaiba-kun and Pegasus will be dueling in a special stadium.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.71,0:20:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to save his little brother, Mokuba-kun,\NKaiba-kun has to beat Pegasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.51,0:20:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But with Pegasus' power to see into people's minds...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.81,0:20:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is not able to even use the Duel Disks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.78,0:20:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: {\c&HFFFFFF&}"Rescue Mokuba! Kaiba VS Pegasus"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:21:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The flask shines bright
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,waiting in the Science Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.57,0:21:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By rubbing our cold hands together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.81,0:21:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They will become warm
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.54,0:21:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.12,0:21:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll shower all over you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.18,0:21:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will support your lonely back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.40,0:21:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.38,0:21:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.04,0:22:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're surrounded by a ring of friendship
